Maintainer: Pengfei Tian <e9tian@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for drawing CATE-propensity-score plots and local IV
    complier-weighted CP plots as diagnostic visualizations for causal
    treatment effect heterogeneity and bracketing relationships. The package
    accompanies Tian, Yang, and Ding (2026), "Bracketing Relationships of
    Weighted Average Treatment Effects", arXiv:2606.11715.
